ard of living without doing irreparable damage to the environment around us. Deep Waters examines the issues involved in the use of nuclear power without over-emphasizing its positive aspects or avoiding its negative aspects.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aHISTORY / Canada / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077357181540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773571815423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773571815/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles